Key Match Events: Jayson Tatum hit a game-winning three-pointer at the buzzer in overtime to give the Celtics a win over the Raptors.
Post-Match Reflections: Jayson Tatum expressed confidence after hitting the game-winning shot.
Al Horford thanked Tatum for helping the Celtics avoid a second overtime period.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was part of a back-to-back series for the Celtics.
Jayson Tatum has been fixing his jumpshot early in the season.
